'''Charles Bernard''' is an [[United States|American]] [[pair skater]]. With partner [[Katie Barnhart]], he is the 1997 [[United States Figure Skating Championships|U.S. junior silver medalist]] and 1997 [[Golden Spin of Zagreb]] champion.
